## 这个流程比较简单，先将Seed设置为随机，且静音Image Refiner & Upscale组， 反复运行直到获得满意的Seed，将其设置为复用最后一次Seed，并打开先前静音的组，运行获得最终大图。

## This workflow is relatively simple. First set the Seed to random and mute the Image Refiner & Upscale group. Run it repeatedly until a satisfactory Seed is obtained. Set it to reuse the last Seed. Unmute the Image Refiner & Upscale group. Run to get the final result. Big picture.
